    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust patches, faded paint, and several dents. Inside, the upholstery requires repair, and some interior components are missing or non-functional. Mechanically, the car starts but will require immediate professional attention to be roadworthy, as there are known issues with the suspension and a persistent oil leak. We recommend a full inspection before purchase to understand the extent of the repairs needed.",
