    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it has been such a reliable companion on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. It drives smoothly and still looks great! If you're looking for a dependable ride that won't let you down, come check it out\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis remains sharp with a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension provide precise turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this driver-focused example has been meticulously maintained, with recent rod bearing service and a fresh valve adjustment. A true analog masterpiece ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Minimal exterior wear. Title in hand. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a sophisticated Deep Sea Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a full portfolio of maintenance records included. The exterior paint retains a brilliant, deep luster, though a discerning eye will note minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well. The interior is a sanctuary of Canberra Beige Dakota Leather; the seats are firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use. All high-tech features, including the 10.2-inch iDrive touchscreen, head-up display, and Harman Kardon premium audio, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the turbocharged inline-six engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, effortless power. Recent preventative maintenance includes a fresh oil service, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The car sits on a set of Continental All-Season tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a complete, honest, and high-performing luxury sedan that bridges the gap between daily utility and executive refinement.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring consistent performance and a sophisticated driving experience. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers exceptional value for the discerning motorist seeking reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value, making it a fantastic choice if you want something dependable and stylish without breaking the bank. I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to really like it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example of this legendary platform. This unit features the high-revving F20C inline-four, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral 9,000 RPM redline. The close-ratio six-speed manual transmission remains crisp, providing short, mechanical throws. It retains its factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution and corner-exit traction. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and fresh synthetic fluids to ensure the VTEC engagement remains sharp. The double-wishbone suspension architecture is intact, offering exceptional turn-in response and chassis communication. While the exterior shows honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust and ready for the canyon roads.",
